{"tid":455520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國旅行團土耳其遇暴雨致車禍　1死10傷","createTime":"2017-11-02T07:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T07:10:05.000Z","uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"deb320075eee1fe274b37787953d57eacc2595db","tid":455520,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"中國駐土耳其伊茲密爾總領館網站消息指，當地時間周日（10月29日）上午9時許，一輛滿載中國遊客的旅遊巴在安塔利亞市Akseki地區因突遇暴雨，導致翻側，造成1名中國遊客死亡、10人受傷，其中2人重傷。目前，兩名重傷遊客在當地醫院接受救治，8名輕傷者已於周二（10月31日）下午出院。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171102/mobile/bkncn-20171102142708863-1102_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171102%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20171102142708863-1102_05011_001.html&d=Od93XWp5wLOUKSfcqLyypG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=4b1ed5f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171102/mobile/bkncn-20171102142708863-1102_05011_001.html</a>"}]}